<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Office 365 Toolkit</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.1.1/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #003747;
            color: #ffffff;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        .navbar {
            background-color: #065465 !important;
        }
        .card {
            background-color: #046276;
            border-color: #06768d;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .card-header {
            background-color: #065465;
            border-bottom-color: #06768d;
        }
        .form-control {
            background-color: #026a81;
            border-color: #06768d;
            color: #ffffff;
        }
        .form-control:focus {
            background-color: #026a81;
            border-color: #06768d;
            color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 0.25rem rgba(6, 118, 141, 0.25);
        }
        .btn-primary {
            background-color: #06768d;
            border-color: #06768d;
        }
        .btn-primary:hover, .btn-primary:focus {
            background-color: #065465;
            border-color: #065465;
        }
        .btn-outline-info {
            color: #06768d;
            border-color: #06768d;
        }
        .btn-outline-info:hover {
            background-color: #06768d;
            color: #ffffff;
        }
        .modal-content {
            background-color: #046276;
            color: #ffffff;
        }
        .modal-header {
            border-bottom-color: #06768d;
        }
        .modal-footer {
            border-top-color: #06768d;
        }
        .btn-secondary {
            background-color: #065465;
            border-color: #065465;
        }
        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background-color: #003747;
            border-color: #003747;
        }
        a {
            color: #06768d;
        }
        a:hover {
            color: #026a81;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">Bitcircuit - Office 365 Toolkit</a>
        </div>
    </nav>
    <div class="container flex-grow-1 d-flex align-items-center">
        <div class="row justify-content-center w-100">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h2 class="text-center mb-0">Azure Tenant Login</h2>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <% if (locals.error) { %>
                            <div class="alert alert-danger" role="alert">
                                <%= error %>
                            </div>
                        <% } %>
                        <form action="/login" method="POST">
                            <div class="mb-3">
                                <label for="tenantid" class="form-label">Tenant ID</label>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="tenantid" name="tenantid" required>
                            </div>
                            <div class="mb-3">
                                <label for="clientid" class="form-label">Client ID</label>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="clientid" name="clientid" required>
                            </div>
                            <div class="mb-3">
                                <label for="clientsecret" class="form-label">Client Secret</label>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="clientsecret" name="clientsecret" required>
                            </div>
                            <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Anmelden</button>
                                <button type="button" class="btn btn-info" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#helpModal">
                                    <i class="fas fa-question-circle"></i> Hilfe
                                </button>
                            </div>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Help Modal -->
    <div class="modal fade" id="helpModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="helpModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <div class="modal-header">
                    <h5 class="modal-title" id="helpModalLabel">Azure App-Registrierung und Berechtigungen</h5>
                    <button type="button" class="btn-close btn-close-white" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <h6>Wie registriert man eine Azure App?</h6>
                    <ol>
                        <li>Melden Sie sich beim <a href="https://portal.azure.com/" target="_blank">Azure Portal</a> an.</li>
                        <li>Navigieren Sie zu "Azure Active Directory" > "App-Registrierungen" > "Neue Registrierung".</li>
                        <li>Geben Sie einen Namen für Ihre Anwendung ein und wählen Sie die entsprechenden Optionen aus.</li>
                        <li>Klicken Sie auf "Registrieren", um die App zu erstellen.</li>
                    </ol>

                    <h6>Erforderliche Berechtigungen:</h6>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Mail.ReadWrite</li>
                        <li>Mail.Send</li>
                        <li>User.Read</li>
                        <li>User.ReadBasic.All</li>
                    </ul>

                    <p>Um diese Berechtigungen hinzuzufügen, gehen Sie zu Ihrer App-Registrierung > "API-Berechtigungen" > "Berechtigung hinzufügen" und wählen Sie die oben genannten Berechtigungen aus.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-footer">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Schließen</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>